{"tid":505714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"又炒！史雲斯怒炒領隊","createTime":"2017-12-21T12:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T03:36:46.000Z","uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f9886c628521795daf79f476065c6e29bb86f92f","tid":505714,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:13:02.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=bVtLeELf695KmgS203iLZf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1f703e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】由於戰績低迷，史雲斯在周三宣佈辭退領隊基文迪。<br />\n<br />\n史雲斯主席侯贊堅斯於聲明中表示：「在季中易帥，是我們最不想做的事。我們在上季經歷過3名領隊，所以給予了基文迪（Paul Clement）最多的時間去扭轉局勢，但現在認為已不能再拖了，是時候作出改變去救亡。」<br />\n<br />\n45歲的基文迪於2017年1月，以拜仁慕尼黑助教的身份入主天鵝，之後帶領史雲斯護級成功，而侯贊堅斯也感謝這名英格蘭藉主帥在上季作出的貢獻。基文迪的副手尼祖基比斯及哈拉比，亦同時間離隊。<br />\n<br />\n史雲斯現時於英超包尾，18戰只得3勝3和12負累積12分，距離安全區域有4分之差，降班形勢水深火熱。他們在周六英超將跟水晶宮上演護級大戰。"},{"pid":"f28cae66e709f2f8aeb255cc9f370ae2c3fa653d","tid":505714,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"仲有咩人可以教？"},{"pid":"70d64239226e6175dfbdbf95f2cb4780c2393fb3","tid":505714,"uid":31269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"屎雲斯依家邊個係有態嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776246ca39e0e0e97cb98f45a8cbed6b88d7728d","tid":505714,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屎雲斯依家邊個係有態嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邦尼都唔錯"},{"pid":"9aa837c500e26257d64ad8fc2b8372bdb237b751","tid":505714,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"試下請普利斯救亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者搵人渣士帶幾件些路迪兵救亡"},{"pid":"06ca93dadea3bf7531bb8b1d2304bee763ba19e8","tid":505714,"uid":33058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T12:30:0